# Device-tree overlay(s) pre-selected in the shipped image's extlinux.conf
# `primary` boot entry, so they are active out of the box. One dtbo basename per
# line ('#' comments allowed); each must be built into /boot via overlay/dtbo.list.
# The bootloader applies these on top of the base DTB, and a user can still pick a
# different overlay in jetson-io, which supersedes this default. These are
# boot-time extlinux overlays, not the flash-time OVERLAY_DTB_FILE that bakes into
# the DTB partition.

# JAJ ships with the dual IMX219 camera enabled by default.
tegra234-p3767-camera-p3768-imx219-dual.dtbo
